\n<Minato Neon>I don't watch TV much anymore. It's more fun to
play with musical instruments...

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (My partner that I saved up money to buy
during my student days)

\n<Minato Neon>Let's stop \F[\V[2]]... Because when we touch, we
forget about time and get completely absorbed in
it.
\n<Minato Neon>Well, should I change my clothes...
\n<Minato Neon>Well, should I change my clothes...
\n<Minato Neon>Well, should I change my clothes...

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (There's nothing inside. I keep it tidy
regularly.)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F] Why is \N[5]-san in my
room?! Huh----!? C-Could it be...

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] Wait, I swear I didn't do
anything! While I was bringing you here and
putting you to sleep because you got drunk at the
afterparty, I also dozed off. I just woke up too!
(3 seconds)
\n<Minato Neon>It's suspicious that \r[ is speaking so quickly...

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] Ugh... No, it's true...
Why would I even make a move on you in the first
place...

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] W-Well then, I'll be
waiting at the parking lot...

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F] Hey... You said you put me
to sleep, right? So... Did \N[5]-san change me
into this?

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] Hey, don't add sound
effects to everything!

\n<Alex>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] The pulse is rising.
That's suspicious.

\n<\N[5]>......I closed my eyes and helped you change
clothes. I didn't do anything.

\n<Alex>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] Broken speech (laughs),
that person is definitely suspicious.

\n<Minato Neon>Hmmm... You say you won't lay a hand on me, but
you sure took a good look, huh?

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] Please spare me... And
you, shitty app, stay quiet.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (I'm making \N[5]-san wait at the
parking lot. Let's change clothes and go out.)

\n<About the marks on the map> About the marks on the map:  White... indicates a
square where map movement occurs \C[14]. Yellow...
indicates a square where events progress \C[0].
Pink... indicates a square where H events occur
\C[0]. Square... indicates a square where you can
change clothes.
